},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T12:37:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70c2f622317392c30e212faa6ae1dd39b2331890","tid":757793,"uid":28366,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T12:40:04.000Z","msg":"4.創造館<br />\n「創造館」由作家余兒於2013年創立，包括其著作《今晚打喪屍》在內，由其出版社出版的作品不少都得到了跨媒體改編的機會，已由奇妙電視購得改編電視劇版權的小說《男人住家飯》也是由創造館出版。<br />\n<br />\n5.次文化堂<br />\n次文化堂為香港出版社，社長則是彭志銘，以出版政治書籍、次文化、普及文化、粵語本字研究書籍知名。<br />\n<br />\n9.田園書店<br />\n營業時間：10:30&ndash;22:00<br />\n地址：旺角西洋菜南街56號<br />\n1976年創辦的香港特色書店,專營港台大陸文史哲藝術社會勵志書。<br />\n<br />\n10.榆林書店<br />\n營業時間：\t11:00&ndash;22:00<br />\n地址：旺角西洋菜南街59號"},{"pid":"ebd909f59ba8aca257cc934ac8df254858a9ad25","tid":757793,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T12:51:06.000Z","msg":"元朗生活書社<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1712924702253200/posts/2085754844970182/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1712924702253200%2Fposts%2F2085754844970182%2F&d=5SQu4Df4Zm6QU7pBGlGX%2BGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=11d3e56e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1712924702253200/posts/2085754844970182/</a>"},{"pid":"a2dd4c0aae7816452dd20efdf4c14f43f075ebdb","tid":757793,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T12:52:34.000Z","msg":"香港文學生活館，鄧小樺搞既<br />\n定期搞活動支持本土文學<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/539912992761739/posts/1823028821116810/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F539912992761739%2Fposts%2F1823028821116810%2F&d=5SQu4Df4Zm6QU7pBGlGX%2BGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=6620a5f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/539912992761739/posts/1823028821116810/</a>"},{"pid":"fe58d642a4aa09a1d35d534f2c91fe66b094ec0b","tid":757793,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T13:08:38.000Z","msg":"旺角博雅小書店<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com